room_title: Escape room "Missing from the Speakeasy" by Escape Hunt in Miami
room_description:
The Roaring Twenties. The era of prohibition. The city has been taken over by a powerful crime boss, and his network of speakeasies and casinos continues to thrive despite the authorities' efforts to take them down.
The lead dancer in a famous cabaret has disappeared under mysterious circumstances. Youâ€™ll have one hour inside the most notorious speakeasy in town. As mafia associates, you have an hour before the show begins to find the dancer.
